					<p style="padding-left: 30px;">B. Payment. Subscriber agrees to pay all applicable fees for Services in effect at the time of sign-up registration and/or renewal, subject to these Terms. Subscriber agrees to update and keep current all of Subscriber&#8217;s billing information, email and all other contact information. It is the Subscriber&#8217;s responsibility to verify that the information submitted is accurate to insure proper billing and continuity of services. All Phase may use Merchant Updater Services to receive updated billing information from participating providers.<br />
