					<p style="padding-left: 30px;">F. Authority. In the event Subscriber is a corporation, limited liability company, Subscribership, joint venture, other business entity or group of individuals, the person registering for or renewing All Phase Services on behalf of Subscriber hereby certifies that he/she has the authority to and does hereby bind the corporation, limited liability company, Subscribership, joint venture or other individuals in this manner and in connection with Subscriber&#8217;s acceptance of all other Terms set forth herein.</p>
