					<p style="padding-left: 30px;">D. Accurate Account Information. Subscriber must continually update and keep accurate and current Subscriber&#8217;s contact information stored and saved on All Phase in order to avoid termination of Subscriber&#8217;s All Phase account(s).<br />
					<p style="padding-left: 30px;">E. Duty to Notify All Phase of Breach. If Subscriber discovers anyone on the All Phase system violating any of these Terms or notices anything suspicious from the All Phase network, Subscriber agrees to report the violation or suspicious activity to support@AllPhase.com for investigation. All Phase reserves the right to and will immediately terminate any account which All Phase concludes to be in violation of any of these Terms.<br />
